32 float OnRoadSearch::GetOrthogonalAngle(float angle, int SEARCH_LINE_CODE)
33 {
34  int angle_ = 0;
35 
36  if(SEARCH_LINE_CODE == LEFT_TO_MID || SEARCH_LINE_CODE == LEFT_TO_RIGHT || SEARCH_LINE_CODE == MID_TO_RIGHT) angle_ = (angle - 90);
37 
38  if(SEARCH_LINE_CODE == RIGHT_TO_MID || SEARCH_LINE_CODE == RIGHT_TO_LEFT || SEARCH_LINE_CODE == MID_TO_LEFT) angle_ = (angle + 90);
39 
40  if(angle_ > 359) angle_ = angle_ % 360;
41 
42  if(angle_ < 0) angle_ = 360 - abs(angle_);
43 
44  return float(angle_);
45 }

88 vector<pair<string,int>> OnRoadSearch::GatherBlackAndWhiteRoadSegments(Mat scanned_line_mat)
89 {
90  vector<pair<string,int>> black_white_road_segments;
91 
92  vector<int> line_segments;
93  line_segments.push_back(-1);
94 
95  for (int i = 0; i < scanned_line_mat.rows; ++i)
96  {
97  for (int j = 0; j < scanned_line_mat.cols; ++j)
98  {
99  int px = (int)scanned_line_mat.at<uchar>(i,j);
100 
101  if(line_segments[line_segments.size()-1] == px)
102  {
103  line_segments.push_back(px);
104  }
105  else
106  {
107  if(px == 255 && line_segments[line_segments.size()-1] != -1)
108  {
109  black_white_road_segments.push_back(make_pair("black",line_segments.size()));
110  }
111  else if(px == 0 && line_segments[line_segments.size()-1] != -1)
112  {
113  black_white_road_segments.push_back(make_pair("white",line_segments.size()));
114  }
115  line_segments.clear();
116  line_segments.push_back(px);
117  }
118  }
119  }
120 
121  if(line_segments[line_segments.size()-1] == 255)
122  {
123  black_white_road_segments.push_back(make_pair("white",line_segments.size()));
124  }
125  else{
126  black_white_road_segments.push_back(make_pair("black",line_segments.size()));
127  }
128 
129  return black_white_road_segments;
130 }

535 void OnRoadSearch::ExtractMinMaxLineElements( vector<LineValidationTable> line, MinMaxLineElements& line_minmax_elements )
536 {
537 
538  if(line.size() > 0)
539  {
540  auto x_it = minmax_element(begin(line),end(line),
541  [&](LineValidationTable& line_point1, LineValidationTable& line_point2)
542  {
543  return line_point1.GetOriginPoint().x < line_point2.GetOriginPoint().x;
544  });
545 
546  auto y_it = minmax_element(begin(line),end(line),
547  [&](LineValidationTable& line_point1, LineValidationTable& line_point2)
548  {
549  return line_point1.GetOriginPoint().y < line_point2.GetOriginPoint().y;
550  });
551 
552  int x_min_id = std::distance(line.begin(), x_it.first);
553  int x_max_id = std::distance(line.begin(), x_it.second);
554  int y_min_id = std::distance(line.begin(), y_it.first);
555  int y_max_id = std::distance(line.begin(), y_it.second);
556 
557  line_minmax_elements = MinMaxLineElements{line[x_min_id].GetOriginPoint(),
558  line[x_max_id].GetOriginPoint(),
559  line[y_min_id].GetOriginPoint(),
560  line[y_max_id].GetOriginPoint(),
561  true};
562  }

575 void OnRoadSearch::SearchForStrongDirectionDifferencesInValidationtables()
576 {
577  found_mid_crossing_ = false;
578  if(mid_line_validation_table_.size()>0){
579  if(mid_line_validation_table_[mid_line_validation_table_.size()-1].GetLabel() > 0)
580  {
581  for(auto it: mid_line_validation_table_)
582  {
583  if( it.GetDirection()>kMinToLeftMidLineDirectionForCrossing_ ||
584  it.GetDirection() < kMaxToLeftMidLineDirectionForCrossing_ ||
585  (it.GetDirection() < kMaxToRightMidLineDirectionForCrossing_ &&
586  it.GetDirection() > kMinToRightMidLineDirectionForCrossing_))
587  {
588  found_mid_crossing_ = true;
589 
590  }
591  }
592  }}
593 
594  found_left_crossing_ = false;
595  if(left_line_validation_table_.size()>0)
596  {
597  int tmp_direction = left_line_validation_table_[0].GetDirection();
598 
599  for(int i=0; i<left_line_validation_table_.size(); i++)
600  {
601  if( left_line_validation_table_[i].GetOriginPoint().y < kMaxCrossingForsightY_) break;
602  int current_direction = left_line_validation_table_[i].GetDirection();
603  int direction_difference = abs(current_direction - tmp_direction);
604 
605  if(direction_difference > kMinOutLineDirectionDifferenceForCrossing_)// && (360 - 80) < direction_difference)
606  {
607  if(current_direction > kMinToLeftLeftLineDirectionForCrossing_ && current_direction < kMaxToLeftLeftLineDirectionForCrossing_)
608  { found_left_crossing_ = true;
609  break;
610  }
611  }
612  tmp_direction = current_direction;
613  }
614 
615  }
616 
617  found_right_crossing_ = false;
618  if(right_line_validation_table_.size()>0)
619  {
620  int tmp_direction = right_line_validation_table_[0].GetDirection();
621  for(int i=0; i<right_line_validation_table_.size(); i++)
622  {
623  if( right_line_validation_table_[i].GetOriginPoint().y < kMaxCrossingForsightY_) break;
624  int current_direction = right_line_validation_table_[i].GetDirection();
625  int direction_difference = abs(current_direction - tmp_direction);
626 
627  if(direction_difference > kMinOutLineDirectionDifferenceForCrossing_)// || (360 - 80) < direction_difference)
628  {
629  if(current_direction > kMinToRightRightLineDirectionForCrossing_ || current_direction < kMaxToRightRightLineDirectionForCrossing_)
630  { found_right_crossing_ = true;
631  break;
632  }
633  }
634  tmp_direction = current_direction;
635  }
636 
637  }
638 }
